---

<section id="implementation" class="section bg-white">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title">Plan de <span class="text-primary-600">Implementare</span></h2>
    <p class="section-subtitle">Un proces simplu și eficient pentru integrarea programului în cultura companiei dumneavoastră</p>
    
    <div class="relative mt-16 animate-on-scroll">
      <!-- Timeline line -->
      <div class="absolute left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 h-full w-1 bg-primary-200 hidden md:block"></div>
      
      <!-- Timeline items -->
      <div class="space-y-12 md:space-y-0">
        <!-- Step 1 -->
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center">
          <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pr-12 md:text-right mb-6 md:mb-0">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Pre-Program</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Sesiune demonstrativă gratuită de 1 oră cu voluntari din echipa dumneavoastră pentru a vă familiariza cu programul și a evalua interesul.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary-500 text-white z-10 mb-6 md:mb-0">
            <span class="font-bold">1</span>
          </div>
          <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pl-12 hidden md:block">
            <img 
              src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1600880292203-757bb62b4baf?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D&auto=format&fit=crop&w=500&q=80" 
              alt="Sesiune demonstrativă" 
              class="w-full h-auto rounded-lg shadow"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Step 2 -->
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center">
          <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pr-12 hidden md:block">
            <img 
              src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1517245386807-bb43f82c33c4?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D&auto=format&fit=crop&w=500&q=80" 
              alt="Prima lună de program" 
              class="w-full h-auto rounded-lg shadow"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary-500 text-white z-10 mb-6 md:mb-0">
            <span class="font-bold">2</span>
          </div>
          <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pl-12">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Luna 1</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Program inițial cu sesiuni zilnice și colectare de feedback pentru a adapta conținutul la nevoile specifice ale echipei dumneavoastră.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Step 3 -->
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center">
          <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pr-12 md:text-right mb-6 md:mb-0">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Luna 2-3</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Continuarea programului cu dezvoltarea progresivă a abilităților și tehnicilor, adaptate în funcție de feedback-ul primit.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary-500 text-white z-10 mb-6 md:mb-0">
            <span class="font-bold">3</span>
          </div>
          <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pl-12 hidden md:block">
            <img 
              src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1551632436-cbf8dd35adfa?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D&auto=format&fit=crop&w=500&q=80" 
              alt="Dezvoltare progresivă" 
              class="w-full h-auto rounded-lg shadow"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Step 4 -->
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center">
          <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pr-12 hidden md:block">
            <img 
              src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1454165804606-c3d57bc86b40?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D&auto=format&fit=crop&w=500&q=80" 
              alt="Evaluare trimestrială" 
              class="w-full h-auto rounded-lg shadow"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary-500 text-white z-10 mb-6 md:mb-0">
            <span class="font-bold">4</span>
          </div>
          <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pl-12">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Sfârșitul Trimestrului</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Evaluare cuprinzătoare a rezultatelor și impactului programului, cu recomandări pentru continuare bazate pe date concrete.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="mt-16 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 animate-on-scroll">
      <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-primary-600">Strategia de Implicare</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary-500 mr-2 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
            <span>Integrarea în orele normale de lucru crește participarea</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary-500 mr-2 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
            <span>Abordarea flexibilă permite non-participanților să continue munca normală</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary-500 mr-2 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
            <span>Introducerea treptată a tehnicilor construiește încredere</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary-500 mr-2 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
            <span>Oportunități regulate de feedback asigură adaptarea la nevoile specifice</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-primary-600">Măsurarea Succesului</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary-500 mr-2 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
            <span>Ratele de participare ale angajaților</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary-500 mr-2 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
            <span>Sondaje de satisfacție la intervale cheie</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary-500 mr-2 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
            <span>Îmbunătățiri auto-raportate ale productivității și stării de bine</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary-500 mr-2 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
            <span>Feedback de la managerii de echipă privind atmosfera la locul de muncă</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>